client.Client\n36: - [ ] Verify Reconciler struct has Scheme field (*runtime.Scheme)\n37: - [ ] Verify client package is imported from sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime/pkg/client\n38: - [ ] Verify runtime package is imported from k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime\n39: - [ ] Verify reconciler package imports are correct\n40: - [ ] Verify struct has proper documentation comments\n41: \n42: **Verification**: Review controller.go and verify Reconciler struct matches design\n43: \n44: ---\n45: \n46: ### Task 4: Implement Reconcile method - Get sandbox resource\n47: - [ ] Verify Reconcile method signature matches controller-runtime Reconciler interface\n48: - [ ] Verify context parameter is accepted\n49: - [ ] Verify req reconcile.Request parameter is accepted\n50: - [ ] Verify agentsv1alpha1.Sandbox is instantiated\n51: - [ ] Verify r.Get(ctx, req.NamespacedName, sandbox) is called\n52: - [ ] Verify apierrors.IsNotFound(err) check is implemented\n53: - [ ] Verify reconcile.Result{}, nil is returned for NotFound errors\n54: - [ ] Verify err is returned for other errors\n55: - [ ] Verify proper error wrapping with context\n56: \n57: **Verification**: Test Reconcile method with non-existent sandbox resource\n58: \n59: ---\n60: \n61: ### Task 5: Implement Reconcile method - Read and validate annotation\n62: - [ ] Verify sandbox.Annotations is accessed\n63: - [ ] Verify LastActivityAnnotationKey is used to lookup annotation\n64: - [ ] Verify exists check is implemented for annotation\n65: - [ ] Verify empty string check is implemented\n66: - [ ] Verify reconcile.Result{}, nil is returned for missing/empty annotation\n67: - [ ] Verify annotation value is extracted correctly\n68: \n69: **Verification**: Test Reconcile method with sandbox without last-activity-time annotation\n70: \n71: ---\n72: \n73: ### Task 6: Implement Reconcile method - Parse last activity time\n74: - [ ] Verify time.Parse(time.RFC3339, lastActivityStr) is called\n75: - [ ] Verify parsing error is handled\n76: 