{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775862194106,"sessionID":"ses_2865e423fffe2OtZiXQDxVHFSC","part":{"id":"prt_d79a29f8d001mt6CKHL8sUg55B","messageID":"msg_d79a2861b001FpGNCZkewqa4s0","sessionID":"ses_2865e423fffe2OtZiXQDxVHFSC","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-cfa20df92c6647fb991588040168c202","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/pkg/workloadmanager/design-gc.md","limit":200},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/pkg/workloadmanager/design-gc.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # Sandbox GC 定时清理机制\n2: \n3: **AR**: AR-008  \n4: **Module**: `pkg/workloadmanager`  \n5: **Language**: Go  \n6: **Size**: S  \n7: **Purpose**: Implement periodic garbage collection for sandbox resources based on idle timeout and TTL expiry.\n8: \n9: ## Architecture\n10: \n11: ### Component Overview\n12: \n13: ```\n14: ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n15: │                     WorkloadManager                         │\n16: │                                                              │\n17: │  ┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐  │\n18: │  │              GarbageCollector                        │  │\n19: │  │  ┌────────────┐  ┌────────────┐  ┌────────────┐     │  │\n20: │  │  │ gcLoop()   │  │ tick()     │  │ deleteSandbox() │  │  │\n21: │  │  │ (ticker)   │  │ (timeout)  │  │ (K8s API + Store) │ │\n22: │  │  └────────────┘  └────────────┘  └────────────┘     │  │\n23: │  └──────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘  │\n24: └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘\n25:          │                        │\n26:          │                        │\n27:          ▼                        ▼\n28: ┌──────────────────┐  ┌──────────────────┐\n29: │  Kubernetes API  │  │     Redis Store  │\n30: │  (Sandbox CRDs)  │  │  (Session Data)  │\n31: └──────────────────┘  └──────────────────┘\n32: ```\n33: \n34: ### Cleanup Triggers\n35: \n36: 1. **Idle Timeout**: Sandboxes with `LastActivityAt < now - DefaultSandboxIdleTimeout` (15 minutes)\n37: 2. **TTL Expiry**: Sandboxes with `ExpiresAt < now`\n38: 3. **Manual Deletion**: Explicit session deletion via API\n39: \n40: ## Data Structures\n41: \n42: ### GarbageCollector\n43: \n44: **File**: `pkg/workloadmanager/garbage_collector.go`\n45: \n46: ```go\n47: type GarbageCollector struct {\n48: \tdynamicClient dynamic.Interface  // Kubernetes dynamic client for CRD operations\n49: \tstoreClient   store.Store        // Redis store for session data\n50: \tinterval      time.Duration      // GC run interval (default: 15s)\n51: \tctx           context.Context    // Context for cancellation\n52: \tcancel        context.CancelFunc // Cancel function for graceful shutdown\n53: }\n54: ```\n55: \n56: ### Cleanup Reasons\n57: \n58: **File**: `pkg/workloadmanager/types/sandbox_types.go`\n59: \n60: ```go\n61: type SandboxCleanupReason string\n62: \n63: const (\n64: \tCleanupReasonManual      SandboxCleanupReason = \"manual\"\n65: \tCleanupReasonIdleTimeout SandboxCleanupReason = \"idle_timeout\"\n66: \tCleanupReasonExpired     SandboxCleanupReason = \"expired\"\n67: )\n68: ```\n69: \n70: ### Audit Entry\n71: \n72: ```go\n73: type CleanupAuditEntry struct {\n74: \tSessionID    string               `json:\"sessionId\"`\n75: \tSandboxID    string               `json:\"sandboxId\"`\n76: \tNamespace    string               `json:\"namespace\"`\n77: \tReason       SandboxCleanupReason `json:\"reason\"`\n78: \tDeletedAt    time.Time            `json:\"deletedAt\"`\n79: \tSuccess      bool                 `json:\"success\"`\n80: \tErrorMessage string               `json:\"errorMessage,omitempty\"`\n81: }\n82: ```\n83: \n84: ## API Contracts\n85: \n86: ### Kubernetes CRD Resources\n87: \n88: The GarbageCollector operates on two CRD types:\n89: \n90: | GVR | Group | Version | Resource |\n91: |-----|-------|---------|----------|\n92: | `agents.x-k8s.io/v1alpha1/sandboxes` | `agents.x-k8s.io` | `v1alpha1` | `sandboxes` |\n93: | `extensions.agents.x-k8s.io/v1alpha1/sandboxclaims` | `extensions.agents.x-k8s.io` | `v1alpha1` | `sandboxclaims` |\n94: \n95: ### Store Interface\n96: \n97: ```go\n98: type Store interface {\n99: \t// ListExpiredSandboxes returns sandboxes with ExpiresAt < before\n100: \tListExpiredSandboxes(ctx context.Context, before time.Time, limit int) ([]*types.SandboxInfo, error)\n101: \t\n102: \t// ListInactiveSandboxes returns sandboxes with LastActivityAt < before\n103: \tListInactiveSandboxes(ctx context.Context, before time.Time, limit int) ([]*types.SandboxInfo, error)\n104: \t\n105: \t// DeleteSandboxBySessionID removes session data from Redis\n106: \tDeleteSandboxBySessionID(ctx context.Context, sessionID string) error\n107: }\n108: ```\n109: \n110: ### SandboxInfo (from Store)\n111: \n112: ```go\n113: type SandboxInfo struct {\n114: \tSessionID           string    `json:\"sessionId\"`\n115: \tSandboxID           string    `json:\"sandboxId\"`\n116: \tSandboxNamespace    string    `json:\"sandboxNamespace\"`\n117: \tKind                string    `json:\"kind\"` // \"Sandbox\" or \"SandboxClaim\"\n118: \tExpiresAt           time.Time `json:\"expiresAt\"`\n119: \tLastActivityAt      time.Time `json:\"lastActivityAt\"`\n120: }\n121: ```\n122: \n123: ## Error Handling\n124: \n125: ### Error Scenarios\n126: \n127: | Scenario | Handling |\n128: |----------|----------|\n129: | Store query fails | Log error, continue to next query |\n130: | K8s API delete fails (NotFound) | Treat as success, delete from store |\n131: | K8s API delete fails (other) | Log error, audit as failure, continue |\n132: | Store delete fails | Log warning (not critical) |\n133: | Context timeout | Cancel current tick, retry next interval |\n134: \n135: ### Error Logging\n136: \n137: All errors are logged with structured fields:\n138: - Session ID\n139: - Sandbox ID\n140: - Namespace\n141: - Reason\n142: - Error message\n143: \n144: ## Testing Strategy\n145: \n146: ### Unit Tests\n147: \n148: **File**: `pkg/workloadmanager/garbage_collector_test.go`\n149: \n150: ```go\n151: package workloadmanager_test\n152: \n153: import (\n154: \t\"context\"\n155: \t\"testing\"\n156: \t\"time\"\n157: \n158: \t. \"github.com/onsi/ginkgo/v2\"\n159: \t. \"github.com/onsi/gomega\"\n160: \t\"k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime\"\n161: \t\"k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime/schema\"\n162: \tdynamicfake \"k8s.io/client-go/dynamic/fake\"\n163: \n164: \t\"github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/workloadmanager\"\n165: )\n166: \n167: var _ = Describe(\"GarbageCollector\", func() {\n168: \tvar (\n169: \t\tfakeDynamicClient *dynamicfake.FakeDynamicClient\n170: \t\tfakeStore         *FakeStore\n171: \t\tgc                *workloadmanager.GarbageCollector\n172: \t\tctx               context.Context\n173: \t)\n174: \n175: \tBeforeEach(func() {\n176: \t\tscheme := runtime.NewScheme()\n177: \t\tfakeDynamicClient = dynamicfake.NewSimpleDynamicClient(scheme)\n178: \t\tfakeStore = NewFakeStore()\n179: \t\tgc = workloadmanager.NewGarbageCollector(fakeDynamicClient, fakeStore, 100*time.Millisecond)\n180: \t\tctx = context.Background()\n181: \t})\n182: \n183: \tAfterEach(func() {\n184: \t\tgc.Stop()\n185: \t})\n186: \n187: \tContext(\"Cleanup of idle sandboxes\", func() {\n188: \t\tIt(\"should delete sandboxes idle for more than timeout\", func() {\n189: \t\t\tsandbox := &types.SandboxInfo{\n190: \t\t\t\tSessionID:        \"test-session\",\n191: \t\t\t\tSandboxID:        \"test-sandbox\",\n192: \t\t\t\tSandboxNamespace: \"default\",\n193: \t\t\t\tKind:             \"Sandbox\",\n194: \t\t\t\tExpiresAt:        time.Now().Add(1 * time.Hour),\n195: \t\t\t\tLastActivityAt:   time.Now().Add(-20 * time.Minute),\n196: \t\t\t}\n197: \t\t\tfakeStore.AddSandbox(sandbox)\n198: \n199: \t\t\tgc.Start()\n200: \t\t\ttime.Sleep(200 * time.Millisecond)\n\n(Showing lines 1-200 of 458. Use offset=201 to continue.)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# Sandbox GC 定时清理机制\n\n**AR**: AR-008  \n**Module**: `pkg/workloadmanager`  \n**Language**: Go  \n**Size**: S  \n**Purpose**: Implement periodic garbage collection for sandbox resources based on idle timeout and TTL expiry.\n\n## Architecture\n\n### Component Overview\n\n```\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│                     WorkloadManager                         │\n│                                                              │\n│  ┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐  │\n│  │              GarbageCollector                        │  │\n│  │  ┌────────────┐  ┌────────────┐  ┌────────────┐     │  │\n│  │  │ gcLoop()   │  │ tick()     │  │ deleteSandbox() │  │  │","truncated":true,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/pkg/workloadmanager/design-gc.md","time":{"start":1775862194092,"end":1775862194104}}}}
