{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775862523876,"sessionID":"ses_2865e423fffe2OtZiXQDxVHFSC","part":{"id":"prt_d79a7a7c9001YDw5q7QLHQBPNO","messageID":"msg_d79a767470010jR0AkYOUymFuR","sessionID":"ses_2865e423fffe2OtZiXQDxVHFSC","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_tool-3ccb6581c6b94b2fa5cd275965cb1676","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# Agentd - 空闲清理控制器\n\nAgentd 是一个 Kubernetes 控制器，负责监控和管理 AgentCube 中的 Sandbox 资源的空闲状态。当 Sandbox 资源在配置的超时时间内没有活动时，Agentd 自动清理该资源，释放计算资源，防止资源浪费。\n\n## 功能特性\n\n- **被动监控**: 通过 Kubernetes Informer 机制被动监听 Sandbox 资源变更\n- **精确调度**: 使用 `RequeueAfter` 实现精确的超时调度，避免频繁轮询\n- **幂等性**: 所有操作都是幂等的，可以安全地重复执行\n- **最小干扰**: 只在必要时触发清理操作，减少对正常运行中的 Sandbox 的影响\n- **注解驱动**: 通过注解进行状态通信，与 workload-manager 协同工作\n\n## 核心组件\n\n- `controller.go`: Reconciler 主控制器实现\n- `controller_test.go`: 控制器单元测试\n- `constants.go`: 常量定义（超时时间、注解键等）\n- `main.go`: 二进制入口点\n\n## 配置参数\n\n### 命令行参数\n\n- `--metrics-bind-address`: 指标端点绑定地址 (默认: `:8080`)\n- `--health-probe-bind-address`: 健康检查端点绑定地址 (默认: `:8081`)\n- `--leader-elect`: 启用领导者选举（默认: `false`）\n\n### 常量定义\n\n- `SessionExpirationTimeout`: 空闲会话超时时间 (默认: `15 minutes`)\n- `LastActivityAnnotationKey`: 用于跟踪最后活动时间的注解键 (`last-activity-time`)\n- `DefaultRequeueInterval`: 默认重新调度间隔 (默认: `30 seconds`)\n\n## 工作原理\n\n1. **资源变更触发**: 当 Sandbox 资源创建、更新或删除时，Kubernetes Informer 触发 Reconcile\n2. **获取资源**: 从 API Server 获取最新的 Sandbox 资源状态\n3. **检查注解**: 读取 `last-activity-time` 注解的值\n4. **解析时间**: 将注解中的 RFC3339 时间字符串解析为 `time.Time`\n5. **计算超时**: `expirationTime = lastActivity + SessionExpirationTimeout`\n6. **判断状态**:\n   - 如果 `now > expirationTime`: 删除 Sandbox 资源\n   - 如果 `now <= expirationTime`: 延迟重新调度，等待到超时时间点\n7. **返回结果**: 返回 `reconcile.Result{RequeueAfter: duration}` 或错误\n\n## 注解说明\n\n### last-activity-time\n\n由 workload-manager 设置的注解，记录 Sandbox 的最后活动时间。\n\n**格式**: RFC3339 (例如: `2026-04-11T07:00:00Z`)\n\n**示例**:\n```yaml\nmetadata:\n  annotations:\n    last-activity-time: \"2026-04-11T07:00:00Z\"\n```\n\n## 错误处理\n\n| 错误类型 | 处理策略 | 说明 |\n|---------|---------|------|\n| 资源不存在 | 返回无错误 | `IsNotFound(err)` |\n| 解析错误 | 延迟重试 | 无效的 RFC3339 时间，延迟 30 秒重试 |\n| API 错误 | 返回错误触发重试 | 网络超时、权限错误 |\n| 删除错误 | 返回错误触发重试 | 资源被锁定 |\n\n## RBAC 权限\n\n需要以下 RBAC 权限：\n\n```yaml\nrules:\n  - apiGroups: [\"agents.x-k8s.io\"]\n    resources: [\"sandboxes\"]\n    verbs: [\"get\", \"list\", \"watch\", \"delete\"]\n  - apiGroups: [\"agents.x-k8s.io\"]\n    resources: [\"sandboxes/status\"]\n    verbs: [\"get\"]\n```\n\n## 运行\n\n### 本地运行\n\n```bash\ngo run ./cmd/agentd \\\n  --metrics-bind-address=:8080 \\\n  --health-probe-bind-address=:8081 \\\n  --leader-elect\n```\n\n### 构建\n\n```bash\ngo build -o agentd ./cmd/agentd\n```\n\n### Kubernetes 部署\n\n参考设计文档中的 Kubernetes Deployment 配置。\n\n## 测试\n\n运行单元测试：\n\n```bash\ngo test ./pkg/agentd -v -cover\n```\n\n预期测试覆盖率: >80%\n\n## 日志\n\n使用 klog 进行日志记录：\n\n```go\nklog.InfoS(\"Sandbox is idle and will be deleted\",\n    \"namespace\", req.Namespace,\n    \"name\", req.Name,\n    \"idleDuration\", time.Since(lastActivity),\n)\n\nklog.ErrorS(err, \"Failed to delete sandbox\",\n    \"namespace\", req.Namespace,\n    \"name\", req.Name,\n)\n```\n\n## 与 workload-manager 的集成\n\nAgentd 与 workload-manager 通过注解协同工作：\n\n1. workload-manager 创建 Sandbox 并设置 `last-activity-time` 注解\n2. 当有活动时，workload-manager 更新 `last-activity-time` 注解\n3. Agentd 监控 Sandbox 并在超时后删除资源\n4. 两个组件通过注解进行通信，无需直接调用\n\n## 架构原则\n\n1. **被动监控**: 通过 Kubernetes Informer 机制被动监听资源变更\n2. **延迟调度**: 使用 `RequeueAfter` 实现精确的超时调度\n3. **幂等性**: 所有操作都是幂等的，可以安全地重复执行\n4. **最小干扰**: 只在必要时触发清理操作\n5. **注解驱动**: 通过注解进行状态通信","filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/pkg/agentd/README.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.\n\nLSP errors detected in other files:\n<diagnostics file=\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/pkg/workloadmanager/gc/collector.go\">\nERROR [200:36] c.storeClient.GetSandbox undefined (type store.Store has no field or method GetSandbox)\nERROR [221:30] a.store.GetSandbox undefined (type store.Store has no field or method GetSandbox)\n</diagnostics>\n\nLSP errors detected in other files:\n<diagnostics file=\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/pkg/workloadmanager/server/server.go\">\nERROR [50:27] undefined: store.NewValkeyStore\n</diagnostics>\n\nLSP errors detected in other files:\n<diagnostics file=\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/pkg/workloadmanager/gc/scheduler_test.go\">\nERROR [26:47] cannot use mockStore (variable of type *mockStore) as store.Store value in argument to NewGCScheduler: *mockStore does not implement store.Store (missing method GetSandboxBySessionID)\nERROR [46:47] cannot use mockStore (variable of type *mockStore) as store.Store value in argument to NewGCScheduler: *mockStore does not implement store.Store (missing method GetSandboxBySessionID)\nERROR [63:47] cannot use mockStore (variable of type *mockStore) as store.Store value in argument to NewGCScheduler: *mockStore does not implement store.Store (missing method GetSandboxBySessionID)\nERROR [79:47] cannot use mockStore (variable of type *mockStore) as store.Store value in argument to NewGCScheduler: *mockStore does not implement store.Store (missing method GetSandboxBySessionID)\nERROR [106:47] cannot use mockStore (variable of type *mockStore) as store.Store value in argument to NewGCScheduler: *mockStore does not implement store.Store (missing method GetSandboxBySessionID)\nERROR [139:47] cannot use mockStore (variable of type *mockStore) as store.Store value in argument to NewGCScheduler: *mockStore does not implement store.Store (missing method GetSandboxBySessionID)\nERROR [168:47] cannot use mockStore (variable of type *mockStore) as store.Store value in argument to NewGCScheduler: *mockStore does not implement store.Store (missing method GetSandboxBySessionID)\nERROR [